================================================================================
Get The Source Code
================================================================================

You can download the latest source code from the GitHub repository:

   $ git clone git://github.com/mbrio/roguelike.git

You can check out the GitHub project page at:

http://github.com/mbrio/roguelike

================================================================================
Requirements
================================================================================

The following applications and libraries are necessary to build this Chromium
extension.

The Closure Library
http://code.google.com/closure/library/

The Closure Compiler
http://code.google.com/closure/compiler/

The JavaScript Closure Templates
http://code.google.com/closure/templates/

The JsDoc Toolkit
http://code.google.com/p/jsdoc-toolkit/

Ant
http://ant.apache.org/

================================================================================
Ant Build File Configuration
================================================================================

Be sure to set the first section of properties within build.xml to match your
computers configuration.

================================================================================
Build
================================================================================

All that is needed is to get the source, enter the directory, and run ant:

   $ git clone git://github.com/mbrio/roguelike.git
   $ cd roguelike
   $ ant
